Red Ball following Bot

It is a group project.

Contributors:
- Neelmani
- Arjun
- Devansh
- Raghunandan
- Pintu

My job was to do image processing.
- Created a bot which follow a red ball
- Used MATLAB for image processing
- Arduino, bluetooth sensor, ultrasonic sensor, camera of android mobile was used to control the movement of bot
- Developed skills like  to do image processing, analyse image data , use MATLAB and arduino for IOT applications.
